description: Submission of reserved matters in respect of design of buildings including levels pursuant to condition 02 of approval under Ref: TP/04/2623/VAR1 for redevelopment of site involving erection of 151 residential units (comprising 51 houses and 100 apartments in 2, 3 and 4 storey buildings and being Phase 2 of redevelopment of Plots 4 & 5 for erection of a total of 429 residential units).
